 Assist audit senior to perform audit of private limited in Hong Kong by using audit software as Caseware Auidt working paper as well as Microsoft office etc 

Job Description :
 assist in analyzing client financial data by using Excel (such as PivotTable) before importing into CaseWare Working Papers software;
 assist in importing the financial data into the CaseWa re Working Paper software;
 assist in performing analytical review procedures by using computer assisted software;
 assist in identifying and assess risk of material misstatement (inherent risk and control risk) after performing analyti cal review procedures;
 assist in calculation of materiality level and calculation of sample size of individual audit area, and assist in sorting out the required sample for substantive tests of the transactions;
 assist in doing any oth er ad hoc information or analytical review on financial data by using computer, such as ageing of trade receivable, trade payable and other seasonal trend of the sale, etc.;
 assist in computing the client's audited financial data before tagging i nto IRD e-filing standard templates;
 assist in importing and tagging audited financial data by using IRD iXBRL Data Preparation Tools before e-filing of tax return to IRD; and
 assist in upload the required forms and supporting documents through IRD e-tax services.

